---
/**
 * RevisionBanner — shown at the top of any module whose frontmatter has
 * `revision_pending: true`. Rendered by PageTitle.astro.
 *
 * Set by the quality pipeline when a module is queued for a teaching-style
 * rewrite. Cleared automatically when the rewrite merges. The intent is
 * transparency: learners see that the content is in flight rather than
 * encountering a confusing v3 punchy-style or pad-bombed module without
 * context.
 *
 * Usage in frontmatter:
 *   revision_pending: true
 */
---

<aside class="revision-banner" aria-label="Module revision notice">
  <div class="revision-banner-inner">
    <span class="revision-banner-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#9881;</span>
    <div class="revision-banner-text">
      <strong>This module is queued for a clarity rewrite.</strong>
      The technical content is accurate, but the prose will be reworked for better
      pedagogy (concrete examples, fewer bullet lists, clearer "why before what"
      explanations). Check back soon — or follow progress at
      <a href="https://github.com/kube-dojo/kube-dojo.github.io/issues/388"
         target="_blank" rel="noopener">issue&nbsp;#388</a>.
    </div>
  </div>
</aside>

<style>
  .revision-banner {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4A3300 0%, #6B4A00 100%);
    border-left: 4px solid #FFB300;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.875rem 1.125rem;
    margin: 0.75rem 0 1.5rem;
    color: #FFF8E1;
  }
  .revision-banner-inner {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.875rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .revision-banner-icon {
    color: #FFB300;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .revision-banner-text {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .revision-banner-text strong {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    color: #FFD54F;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .revision-banner-text a {
    color: #FFD54F;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  .revision-banner-text a:hover {
    color: #FFE082;
  }
</style>
